# Router Service Boundaries

For backend API changes, separate transport concerns from business logic.

- Routers (`backend/app/routers/**`) handle endpoint wiring, schema parsing, auth deps, and HTTP mapping.
- Feature services (`backend/app/features/**`) own domain rules, orchestration, sequencing, and non-trivial validation.
- Extract to feature services when a handler becomes multi-entity, conditional-heavy, or reusable.
